    },
    {
      "id": "chapter-5",
      "title": "Tradeoffs & Constraints",
      "slides": [
        {
          "id": "widget-05",
          "label": "The Invisible Tool Problem",
          "type": "narrative",
          "base": {
            "heading": "The Invisible Tool Problem",
            "body": "I never formally pitched the tool\u2014it worked so well that no one realized it existed. That invisibility came with both power and limitations.",
            "readings": {
              "A": {
                "label": "Solo Impact",
                "content": [
                  "No onboarding needed",
                  "No one else used it"
                ]
              },
              "B": {
                "label": "Constraints",
                "content": [
                  "No time for docs",
                  "Tool remained internal"
                ]
              },
              "C": {
                "label": "Tradeoffs",
                "content": [
                  "Saved my bandwidth",
                  "No visibility"
                ]
              },
              "D": {
                "label": "What I Learned",
                "content": [
                  "Surface internal wins early"
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "steps": [
            {
              "body": {
                "add": [
                  "A powerful internal system isn\u2019t useful if no one else can see it."
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "chapter-6",
      "title": "Impact & Evolution",
      "slides": [
        {
          "id": "widget-06",
          "label": "Scaling Without Headcount",
          "type": "narrative",
          "base": {
            "heading": "Scaling Without Headcount",
            "body": "This tool let me double output, maintain quality, and support business needs without requiring another frontend hire for two years.",
            "readings": {
              "A": {
                "label": "Impact",
                "content": [
                  "+50% output",
                  "0 missed deadlines"
                ]
              },
              "B": {
                "label": "Longevity",
                "content": [
                  "Used over multiple years",
                  "Maintained solo"
                ]
              },
              "C": {
                "label": "Handoff Blocked",
                "content": [
                  "Layoff was sudden",
                  "Told to wipe and retain laptop"
                ]
              },
              "D": {
                "label": "Lesson",
                "content": [
                  "Prepare for visibility even in high output scenarios"
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "steps": [
            {
              "body": {
                "add": [
                  "This system worked because it was invisible. That\u2019s also why it didn\u2019t last."
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
